org.rapidcontext.util

Interface HttpUtil.METHOD

  • Enclosing interface:
    HttpUtil

    public static interface HttpUtil.METHOD
    The HTTP methods as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), RFC5789 (PATCH) and RFC4918 (WebDAV).
